      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LINDENOW BUFFY (4) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Missed the frame latest (26.07) when fourth over 460m at Warragul in a Restricted WIN. Looks the one to beat with even luck. OLD HABITS (7) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (25.06) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Rates a winning chance on best. MISS KARIS (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 510m behind Dr. Exclaim (29.53) in a T3 RSTW. The form out of her last race has been franked. Likely to play a prominent role. CHORUS LINE (3) was well supported last time but could only manage third (23.22), beaten 6 lengths. Deserves a win and gets his chance.",
